<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero text-white text-center" style="background:linear-gradient(rgba(0,94,184,0.9),rgba(0,94,184,0.95)),url('/img/about-master-hero.jpg') center/cover no-repeat; min-height:70vh; display:flex; align-items:center;">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="display-2 fw-bold">About Make-A-Wish</h1>
      <p class="lead fs-3">Tens of thousands of volunteers, donors and supporters help us grant the wish of every child diagnosed with a critical illness.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">

        <!-- STICKY SIDE NAVIGATION -->
        <div class="col-lg-3 about-nav">
          <div class="list-group list-group-flush">
            <a href="#mission"      class="list-group-item list-group-item-action py-3">Our Mission</a>
            <a href="#history"      class="list-group-item list-group-item-action py-3">Our History</a>
            <a href="#timeline"     class="list-group-item list-group-item-action py-3">Timeline</a>
            <a href="#structure"    class="list-group-item list-group-item-action py-3">Local & Global Structure</a>
            <a href="#funds"        class="list-group-item list-group-item-action py-3">Managing Our Funds</a>
            <a href="#leadership"   class="list-group-item list-group-item-action py-3">Leadership</a>
            <a href="#careers"      class="list-group-item list-group-item-action py-3">Careers</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
        <div class="col-lg-9">

          <!-- OUR MISSION -->
          <div id="mission" class="mb-5 pb-5 border-bottom">
            <h2 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
            <p class="fs-4 lead">We grant the wish of every child diagnosed with a critical illness. In the U.S. and its territories, a wish is granted every 34 minutes.</p>
            <p class="fs-5">A wish can be that spark that helps these brave children believe anything is possible — and gives them the strength to fight harder. This one belief guides everything we do.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- OUR HISTORY -->
          <div id="history" class="mb-5 pb-5 border-bottom">
            <h2 class="text-primary fw-bold mb-4">Our History</h2>
            <p class="fs-5 mb-4">For children diagnosed with critical illnesses, a wish come true can be a crucial turning point. This impact is why we are driven to make every eligible child’s wish come true.</p>

            <div class="row align-items-center g-5 mb-5">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <h3>1980 – Chris Greicius</h3>
                <p>Make-A-Wish traces its inspiration to Christopher James Greicius, a 7-year-old boy battling leukemia who wished to be a police officer. In 1980, his Phoenix community made it happen. Chris passed away just days later, but his wish created a movement that has transformed millions of lives.</p>
                <blockquote class="fst-italic text-muted border-start border-primary border-5 ps-4 mt-4">
                  “He was only seven years, 269 days old when he died. But he taught me about being a man, even though he was only a boy.”<br><small>— Tommy Austin, Make-A-Wish co-founder</small>
                </blockquote>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <img src="/img/Chris_Uniform_r.jpg" class="img-fluid rounded shadow" alt="Chris Greicius">
              </div>
            </div>

            <h4 class="mt-5">1981 – The First Official Wish: Bopsy Salazar</h4>
            <p>Frank “Bopsy” Salazar, age 7, became the first official Make-A-Wish child. The Phoenix and Anaheim Fire Departments made him a firefighter and took his family to Disneyland — the very first Disney wish.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- TIMELINE -->
          <!-- TIMELINE – UPGRADED & GORGEOUS -->
<div id="timeline" class="mb-5 pb-5">
  <h2 class="text-primary fw-bold text-center mb-5 display-5">Our Journey of Hope</h2>

  <div class="container position-relative">
    <!-- Vertical Line -->
    <div class="position-absolute top-0 bottom-0 start-50 translate-middle-x" style="width:6px; background:linear-gradient(to bottom, #00a7e1, #005eb8); border-radius:3px; z-index:1;"></div>

    <div class="row g-5">

      <!-- 1980 -->
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
        <div class="d-flex flex-row-reverse flex-lg-row align-items-center">
          <div class="flex-grow-1 text-end text-lg-start pe-lg-5">
            <div class="timeline-year bg-primary text-white rounded-pill d-inline-block px-4 py-2 shadow-lg">1980</div>
            <h4 class="mt-3">Chris Greicius’ Wish</h4>
            <p class="text-muted">A 7-year-old boy battling leukemia wished to be a police officer. His community made it happen — and unknowingly sparked a global movement.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-dot bg-white border border-5 border-primary rounded-circle shadow" style="width:60px; height:60px; z-index:2; flex-shrink:0;">
            <i class="bi bi-star-fill text-primary fs-3 position-absolute top-50 start-50 translate-middle"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="d-none d-lg-block" style="width:50%;"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 1981 -->
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
          <div class="d-lg-none" style="width:50%;"></div>
          <div class="timeline-dot bg-white border border-5 border-primary rounded-circle shadow" style="width:60px; height:60px; z-index:2; flex-shrink:0;">
            <i class="bi bi-heart-fill text-danger fs-3 position-absolute top-50 start-50 translate-middle"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-grow-1 ps-lg-5 text-start">
            <div class="timeline-year bg-danger text-white rounded-pill d-inline-block px-4 py-2 shadow-lg">1981</div>
            <h4 class="mt-3">First Official Wish</h4>
            <p class="text-muted">Frank “Bopsy” Salazar becomes the first official wish kid — a firefighter for a day and the very first Disney wish.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 1983 -->
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
        <div class="d-flex flex-row-reverse flex-lg-row align-items-center">
          <div class="flex-grow-1 text-end text-lg-start pe-lg-5">
            <div class="timeline-year bg-success text-white rounded-pill d-inline-block px-4 py-2 shadow-lg">1983</div>
            <h4 class="mt-3">Official Incorporation</h4>
            <p class="text-muted">Make-A-Wish Foundation of America is officially born.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-dot bg-white border border-5 border-success rounded-circle shadow" style="width:60px; height:60px; z-index:2;">
            <i class="bi bi-building fs-3 position-absolute top-50 start-50 translate-middle text-success"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="d-none d-lg-block" style="width:50%;"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 1993 -->
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
          <div class="d-lg-none" style="width:50%;"></div>
          <div class="timeline-dot bg-white border border-5 border-warning rounded-circle shadow" style="width:60px; height:60px; z-index:2;">
            <i class="bi bi-globe fs-3 position-absolute top-50 start-50 translate-middle text-warning"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-grow-1 ps-lg-5 text-start">
            <div class="timeline-year bg-warning text-dark rounded-pill d-inline-block px-4 py-2 shadow-lg">1993</div>
            <h4 class="mt-3">Going Global</h4>
            <p class="text-muted">Make-A-Wish International is formed — now serving 50 countries.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2020 -->
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
        <div class="d-flex flex-row-reverse flex-lg-row align-items-center">
          <div class="flex-grow-1 text-end text-lg-start pe-lg-5">
            <div class="timeline-year bg-info text-white rounded-pill d-inline-block px-4 py-2 shadow-lg">2020</div>
            <h4 class="mt-3">40 Years of Wishes</h4>
            <p class="text-muted">Celebrating 40 years and over 500,000 wishes granted worldwide.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-dot bg-white border border-5 border-info rounded-circle shadow" style="width:60px; height:60px; z-index:2;">
            <i class="bi bi-cake2-fill text-info fs-3 position-absolute top-50 start-50 translate-middle"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="d-none d-lg-block" style="width:50%;"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 2025 – Today -->
      <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
          <div class="d-lg-none" style="width:50%;"></div>
          <div class="timeline-dot bg-white border border-5 border-primary rounded-circle shadow position-relative" style="width:80px; height:80px; z-index:2;">
            <i class="bi bi-stars text-primary fs-1 position-absolute top-50 start-50 translate-middle"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-grow-1 ps-lg-5 text-start">
            <div class="timeline-year bg-primary text-white rounded-pill d-inline-block px-4 py-3 shadow-lg fs-4">2025 & Beyond</div>
            <h4 class="mt-3">The Journey Continues</h4>
            <p class="text-muted fw-bold">With supporters like YOU, Make-A-Wish is growing stronger every day — granting more wishes than ever before.</p>
            <a href="/donate" class="btn btn-wish mt-3">Be Part of Our Future</a>
          </div>
        </div>
